name: 02_Calories: Verify the user can edit the nutrient and the new value gets reflected on the dashboard. -- @1.1

steps.name: Given I navigate to homepage
When I enter username as "testUser"
And I enter password as "Test1234"
And I click on Continue button
And I click on Add Nutrient button on Home page
And I enter "Carbs" value as "20.0"
And I verify "Carbs" got added with value "20.0" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I click on Add Nutrient button on Home page
And I enter "Fat" value as "4.5"
And I verify "Fat" got added with value "4.5" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I click on Add Nutrient button on Home page
And I enter "Alcohol" value as "1.07"
And I verify "Alcohol" got added with value "1.07" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I click on Add Nutrient button on Home page
And I enter "Sugar Alcohol" value as "12.5"
And I verify "Sugar Alcohol" got added with value "12.5" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I update the "Carbs" value as "-4"
And I click on Submit button to add the Nutrient value
And I verify "Carbs" got added with value "-4" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I update the "Fat" value as "3"
And I click on Submit button to add the Nutrient value
And I verify "Fat" got added with value "3" on Nutrients Dashboard
And I update the "Protein" value as "0.25"
And I click on Submit button to add the Nutrient value
And I verify "Protein" got added with value "0.25" on Nutrients Dashboard

fullName: 02_Calories Calculation functionality: 02_Calories: Verify the user can edit the nutrient and the new value gets reflected on the dashboard.
